# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Project-specific: internal docs and planning (not for public GitHub)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Exclude docs/ by default, but re-include the two extension references
# that are genuinely useful for readers on GitHub.
docs/*
!docs/adapter_pattern.md
!docs/pillar3_pdf_spec.md
project guidence.md
PROGRESS.md

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Project-specific: raw data and local DB
# (too large and/or source-owned; reproducible via scripts/download_sources
# and `python cli.py ingest ...`)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
data/
benchmarks.db

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Project-specific: generated outputs
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Default: outputs/ not tracked. Exception: the four Q3 2025 final
# deliverables are committed so GitHub visitors can see example output
# without having to run the pipeline themselves. Future cycles can either
# add their period-specific whitelist entries or keep the deliverables
# out of git.
outputs/*
!outputs/reports/
outputs/reports/*
!outputs/reports/Report_Q3_2025_final.docx
!outputs/reports/Report_Q3_2025_final.html
!outputs/reports/Report_Q3_2025_final_Board.md
!outputs/reports/Report_Q3_2025_final_Technical.md
!outputs/spot_check_verification.md
